INSTALL ECHOES

1 - Using make:
---------------
Go to src and run: 'make'

2 - Using command-line and GCC:
-------------------------------
Go to src and run: 'g++ -Wall Echoes.cpp Echoes.h main.cpp -o echoes'

3 - Creating libs:
g++ -c -Wall -Werror -fpic Echoes.cpp
g++ -shared -o libechoes.so Echoes.o

And......
...........
It's done.
